{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"203-bunty-aur-bubbly","title":"बंटी और बबली","description":"बंटी को साबुन बिलकुल भी नहीं भाता। इसलिए, वह नहाना नहीं चाहती। एक रात उसने एक सपना देखा। उसके बाद क्या हुआ?","language":"Hindi","langCode":"hi","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Rajesh Khar"],"illustrators":["Sorit Gupto"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/203-bunty-aur-bubbly"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/720260/size3/bfaca307e321a40d4fce0bf9bade9047.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/720260/size6/bfaca307e321a40d4fce0bf9bade9047.jpg"},"audio":{"src":"https://storage.googleapis.com/story-weaver-e2e-production/stories/203/audios/story/203-bunty-aur-bubbly.mp3","cues":null},"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2398/size6/9907217108246f4eb01c1ac7f252464b.jpg","text":"बंटी को तितलियों के साथ खेलना अच्छा लगता है।","words":[[1,"बंटी"],[2,"को"],[3,"तितलियों"],[4,"के"],[5,"साथ"],[6,"खेलना"],[7,"अच्छा"],[8,"लगता"],[9,"है।"]]},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2399/size6/3cfef50c731271c06bc7df15adfad696.jpg","text":"और चिड़ियों के साथ भी।","words":[[10,"और"],[11,"चिड़ियों"],[12,"के"],[13,"साथ"],[14,"भी।"]]},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2400/size6/0b2cc2ad4ba1e7c14ab8f85d1cc92a02.jpg","text":"उसे कागज़ की नाव से खेलना भी अच्छा लगता है।","words":[[15,"उसे"],[16,"कागज़"],[17,"की"],[18,"नाव"],[19,"से"],[20,"खेलना"],[21,"भी"],[22,"अच्छा"],[23,"लगता"],[24,"है।"]]},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static